Package: hazer
Title: Identifying Foggy and Cloudy Images by Quantifying Hazeness
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Bijan", "Seyednasrollah", email = "bijan.s.nasr@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The hazer packages, provides few functions to estimate hazeness based on RGB bands. It returns a hazeness factor, varying from 0 to 1, as metric for fogginess and cloudiness. The library contains few functions to estimate brighness and darkness raster of and RGB image.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
